if test "kernel1" = "${ACTIVATED_KERNEL_NAME}"; 
then setenv image_address 0xf80000; 
setenv bootargs "${bootargs} root=rootfs1 debug=1"; 
else setenv bootargs "${bootargs} root=rootfs0 debug=1"; 
fi; sf read ${loadaddr} ${image_address} 0xE00000; bootm
